{"tid":46254,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"邊種激光矯視好","createTime":"2016-12-19T13:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T16:57:07.000Z","uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cad0ed26f493f607afadba8abd5bd58a48b9d35a","tid":46254,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"傳統個種同微笑個隻 有無人做過 邊隻會安全啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc6298a4ec34d82b2453a2458ea8e365b51abb3","tid":46254,"uid":25214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"我都想知"},{"pid":"27af96b9a230332039b78dfcf08cef7c14d4fd26","tid":46254,"uid":36756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:00:28.000Z","msg":"唔用最好"},{"pid":"7548581b2a67c208833ee2930e51d76975b5fb24","tid":46254,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"我做左半年 但唔知自己做邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783df87e2eb128121b0a072cb192ecd29b0403b9","tid":46254,"uid":20557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:19:04.000Z","msg":"做左smile大半年，單眼睇遠野唔算特別清，佢話我有25遠視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩隻眼一齊睇又ok，比我揀多次都係會做，當然亦有人做完失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f88ce48c47380bd7c025d90d61750ed45d02a3","tid":46254,"uid":20557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"Lasik 傷口大d，但係會準d，不過都係睇運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d25e8f7f07bd5c1a1ba5ff655e735f0193083d","tid":46254,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:40:27.000Z","msg":"聽人講第一批做lasik過咗十幾廿年開始岀現後遺症？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a22b39250b36161c1e0ab09b5e183a960e9567e","tid":46254,"uid":20557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:03:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽人講第一批做lasik過咗十幾廿年開始岀現後遺症？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個內容農場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLasik 有好多代，而且你又點知以前d人用有刀定無刀，都係叫lasik<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2845ed3d77dab479f3e3a04d80e574585387e741","tid":46254,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽人講第一批做lasik過咗十幾廿年開始岀現後遺症？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個內容農場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLasik 有好多代，而且你又點知以前d人用有刀定無刀，都係叫lasik<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽阿叔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過同佢唔熟無問清楚"},{"pid":"e43a1e5743d66fd0035fda22dab6646ff299e434","tid":46254,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:27:41.000Z","msg":"微笑唔會咁眼乾<br />\n但貴啲"},{"pid":"c04642d961554b48643255acc58d5c9dbce338e1","tid":46254,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"要驗下睇你眼底幾厚同近視散光幾深先知做唔做到smile"},{"pid":"5afa7f0e548c48ea2a0e546a67d3341e38c3cd7d","tid":46254,"uid":66844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"我係香港矯視中心做smile ，做咗2萬7，我係今年6月尾做手術，起初做完手術第一個星期個醫生話我有7成視力，1個月後已經零散光零近視<br />\n<br />\n利申：本身右眼900幾度左眼800幾度近視，75度散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7611bc5b429cfff896d0aeaf3591a63e9c27c5","tid":46254,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係香港矯視中心做smile ，做咗2萬7，我係今年6月尾做手術，起初做完手術第一個星期個醫生話我有7成視力，1個月後已經零散光零近視<br />\n<br />\n利申：本身右眼900幾度左眼800幾度近視，75度散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之後有冇特別眼乾/累d"},{"pid":"634e3f0068d4edaa845616e40d01bb30c749bf1c","tid":46254,"uid":62030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"邊種都唔好"},{"pid":"14b463d0a979368aff432437364157a969f07cee","tid":46254,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊種都唔好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解 有咩根據咁講"},{"pid":"62cd15dc91c84310ccb2c1772fb30b8eb6076990","tid":46254,"uid":47473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:22:54.000Z","msg":"我諗無人會做過哂兩種，左右眼唔同方法咩&hellip;我睇哂咁多資料，醫院會話smile唔好，診所會話smile好好多。<br />\n眯外國資料就話lasek好過lasik, 不過香港醫生唔多肯做<br />\n<br />\n利申：最後做左lasik"},{"pid":"d88192715ea9df0f445af3a161185f3068903216","tid":46254,"uid":59479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:34:44.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"63bf7bfc05be98d137fef4108582101ab384fa8a","tid":46254,"uid":27024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:38:47.000Z","msg":"留名想做，不過等到25歲先"},{"pid":"d3b8be6ce7a2f9ba198249c0a71995c68ab23dac","tid":46254,"uid":66844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係香港矯視中心做smile ，做咗2萬7，我係今年6月尾做手術，起初做完手術第一個星期個醫生話我有7成視力，1個月後已經零散光零近視<br />\n<br />\n利申：本身右眼900幾度左眼800幾度近視，75度散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之後有冇特別眼乾/累d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無咩特別眼乾同累，做完手術第一個星期係辛苦啲，睇嘢好似有層霧遮住，每過一個星期就好啲啲，慢慢無晒，同埋幫我做手術個醫生佢自己都有做smile"},{"pid":"82e8031194f1ba93976dffb0c6456032e474907d","tid":46254,"uid":66844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗無人會做過哂兩種，左右眼唔同方法咩&hellip;我睇哂咁多資料，醫院會話smile唔好，診所會話smile好好多。<br />\n眯外國資料就話lasek好過lasik, 不過香港醫生唔多肯做<br />\n<br />\n利申：最後做左lasik</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSmile手術時間快，新技術但有限要係1千度近視以下同唔係遠視先做到，同埋貴啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd0cd80284d434618755207e02c47014c2a6ff1","tid":46254,"uid":20557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"比多個醫生既講法你參考，當你隻眼兩樣都做得。<br />\n幫我做smile既醫生問我係咪要考機師，消防，係既就做lasik,唔係做smile, 最後做smile25度遠視好夠用。<br />\n<br />\n你衰運起上黎邊樣都有機會失敗，失敗唔係指感染，呢d萬中無一。係指做完都有百幾度。"},{"pid":"0ae7240267e1ebd0055b6927837891ba498a1465","tid":46254,"uid":66844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:02:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比多個醫生既講法你參考，當你隻眼兩樣都做得。<br />\n幫我做smile既醫生問我係咪要考機師，消防，係既就做lasik,唔係做smile, 最後做smile25度遠視好夠用。<br />\n<br />\n你衰運起上黎邊樣都有機會失敗，失敗唔係指感染，呢d萬中無一。係指做完都有百幾度。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做手術一定係有風險"},{"pid":"b01b6854fca9b40745b343ebd1b16647605ce66c","tid":46254,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c9476e10a378609c5b41c066b27edeba8c7ca1f8","tid":46254,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:49:38.000Z","msg":"我老細唔知幾多年前做LASIK定LASEK<br />\n而家一隻眼D近視突然間番哂黎<br />\n佢仲話佢有個朋友同佢同一狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a080a8ac5ea4af7e621f83358d549aa09d7c6a78","tid":46254,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:56:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老細唔知幾多年前做LASIK定LASEK<br />\n而家一隻眼D近視突然間番哂黎<br />\n佢仲話佢有個朋友同佢同一狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下， 有冇下文？"}]}